thread.title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Overseas Chinese Town issues 2018 second tranche corporate bonds worth 5 bln yuan

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Overseas Chinese Town issues 2018 second tranche corporate bonds worth 5 bln yuan

organizations.name: reuters) - shenzhen overseas chinese town co ltd

text:
Feb 7(Reuters) - Shenzhen Overseas Chinese Town Co Ltd
* Says it issues 5-year 2018 second tranche corporate bonds worth 2 billion yuan, with coupon rate of 5.54 percent
* Says it issues 7-year 2018 second tranche corporate bonds worth 3 billion yuan, with coupon rate of 5.74 percent
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/ttHAXf
